See INSTALL for package build notes.


The following steps, briefly explain how to setup and run a Virtual Machine:


1. Creating a VM:

   $ tools/vm_create /home/user/test_vm 10 64


2. Installing a bootloader:

   $ lavm_binst boot.bin bootloader /home/user/test_vm/storage/00storage


3. Installing a kernel:

   $ lavm_binst kernel.bin kernel /home/user/test_vm/storage/00storage


4. Running a Virtual Machine:

   $ lavm /home/user/test_vm


5. Accessing Virtual Machine Console:

   $ lavm console

